Description: Usage data collection library for HiFiBerry
 This package provides a Python library for collecting usage statistics
 and analytics data for HiFiBerry devices and services.
 .
 The library includes functionality for:
  - Anonymous usage data collection
  - Privacy-aware statistics gathering
  - Data transmission and reporting
 .
 This is the Python 3 version of the package.
